        <updateDate>2019-09-03T18:25:39Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Hospital Competition Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a series of programs and requirements relating to hospital costs, payments, and infrastructure, including a requirement for&nbsp;hospitals, as a condition of Medicare participation, to publish the prices charged for specified services that are highly utilized.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
